body_html:
My point is that you appear to trying to run the training part of your graph rather than the inference part? Is this correct? The set of ops included in ios is limited to training, so you'll have to play with the makefile to add more ops to the build. See:
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/README.md
and search for other issues. I think your issue is a duplicate of
#2929

body:
My point is that you appear to trying to run the training part of your graph rather than the inference part? Is this correct? The set of ops included in ios is limited to training, so you'll have to play with the makefile to add more ops to the build. See:
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/README.md
and search for other issues. I think your issue is a duplicate of
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/2929
